<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      header {
        background-color: #333;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      header h1 {
        color: white;
      }
      .container {
        margin: 0 auto;
        width: 80%;
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 5px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        color: #fff;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding: 20px 0;
        background: purple;
      }
      .content {
        margin-top: 20px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .content p {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #777;
        border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding: 20px 0;
      }
      .highlight {
        color: #4caf50;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <h1>Learning Management System</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="header">Order Confirmation</h2>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Dear <b><%= user.name %></b> ,</p>

          <p>Your order details are as follows:</p>

          <p><strong class="highlight">Order ID:</strong> <%= order.uuid %></p>
          <p>
            <strong class="highlight">Course Name:</strong> <%= order.course %>
          </p>
          <p><strong class="highlight">Price:</strong> â‚¹ <%= order.price %></p>
          <p><strong class="highlight">Date:</strong> <%= order.date %></p>

          <p>
            Thank you for purchasing our course, <%= order.name %> We're
            thrilled to have you on board and excited to be a part of your
            learning journey
          </p>

          <p>
            As you dive into the material, we hope you find the content
            engaging, insightful, and valuable for achieving your goals. Our
            team has put a lot of effort into creating a comprehensive and
            user-friendly experience, and we're confident that you'll gain a lot
            from it
          </p>

          <p>
            Should you have any questions or need assistance along the way,
            please don't hesitate to reach out. We're here to support you every
            step of the way
          </p>

          <p>
            Wishing you all the best as you embark on this educational
            adventure. We're excited to see where this journey takes you!
          </p>

          <p>Thank you once again, and happy learning!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
          <p>
            If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at
            <a href="mailto:[Support Email]">www.mohdshahid303@gmail.com</a>.
          </p>
          <p class="highlight">
            Thank you for choosing our Learning Management System!
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
